# Public env rule:
# Only use NEXT_PUBLIC_ for browser-safe values such as site URL, publishable keys, public analytics IDs, and Supabase anon URL/key.
# Never expose service role keys, webhook secrets, private tokens, or buyer/lead data through NEXT_PUBLIC_ variables.
